Name: TRADEMARK
Explanation: A UNIQUE NAVAL OPERATIONS DESIGNATOR TO A TARGET BY THE UNIT GAINING CONTACT OR BY SENIOR OPERATIONAL COMMANDERS.

Name: COMPONENT TARGET IDENTIFIER
Explanation: THE IDENTIFIER ASSIGNED TO A TARGET BY A COMPONENT.

Name: SHIP TARGET IDENTITY
Explanation: THE CODE FOR THE IDENTITY OF A SURFACE SHIP.

Name: TARGET DESIRED MEAN POINT OF IMPACT (DMPI) IDENTIFIER
TARGET IDENTIFIER, ABBREVIATED
Explanation: THE UNIQUE IDENTIFIER OF A TARGET.

Name: DESIRED MEAN POINT OF IMPACT (DMPI) IDENTIFIER
Explanation: THE UNIQUE IDENTIFIER OF THE DESIRED MEAN POINT OF IMPACT (DMPI).
